;----- $3120: Toggle I/O bit 7 with delay $21 (one half-cycle) -------------
; Clear bit 7 for $21 counts, then set bit 0 for $21 counts.
; This creates a square wave with period proportional to $21.
;
$3120> A5 21:	LDA $21		;
